---
title: Fried Chicken Burger and Cheesy Chips with crispy bacon and spicy aioli
description: Chicken, bacon and chips. It's a pretty unbeatable combination if you ask us. Lashings of slightly spicy aioli for the burgers and mouth-watering melted cheese for the chips make this meal even more enticing.
